<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/nathan-moores> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Nathan is an experienced project, programme and portfolio manager with over 20 years experience leading multi-organisational change and improvements across corporate services in challenging organisational environments, and leading shared services projects.  Nathan started his career in conservation in Natural England, and then led organisational transformation in the UK Space Agency before moving onto corporate services integration in the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs (DEFRA). Since moving on from DEFRA, Nathan has led transformation programmes and overseen the implementation and improvement of Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) systems across the Civil Service, at the Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy, (which preceded the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero, Department for Business and Trade and the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology). Nathan has been the Director of Shared Services for Government since May 2021."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
